"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a clear and reiterated voice:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brayed in the best manner:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IKtt:) said only of a camel advanced in age: (S, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nqD","text_ar":"نقض"},{"kind":"text","text":":)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroqarapN","text_ar":"قَرْقَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the inf. n., (S, * M, K, *) and the simple subst. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroqaArN","text_ar":"قَرْقَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraAqiru","text_ar":"قَرَاقِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of the former of these ns. (S.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroqarato","text_ar":"قَرْقَرَتْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a pigeon,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAmap","text_ar":"حَمَامَة"},{"kind":"text","text":",) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cooed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uttered its cry:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uttered a hind of cry:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) the inf. n. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroqarapN","text_ar":"قَرْقَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroqariyrN","text_ar":"قَرْقَرِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) which latter IJ says is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolaliyolN","text_ar":"فَعْلَلِيْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", thus making it a quadriliteralradical word, (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroqaArN","text_ar":"قَرْقَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroqaArN","text_ar":"قَرْقَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which last is a simple subst. as well as an inf. n., and so is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroqrapN","text_ar":"قَرْقرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (El-Hasan Ibn-'Abd-Allah El-Kátib El-Isbahánee.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a domestic hen)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uttered a reiterated cry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cackling."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Hr, M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","M","K","IKtt"]}]}}